{"title":"公社春天我们画","authors":["马成忠"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":9,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社春天我们画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽来安县长山公社  马成忠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山听我们的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南岭种上桃杏梨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北坡播下桐和茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山间苍松挺风立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"园内翠竹美如画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃岭披上绿衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山花果挂彩霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水听我们的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村前挖口跃进塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄后打道红旗坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沟渠纵横如蛛网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自流灌溉水利化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修座水库安电站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电灯照亮社员家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地听我们的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银锄挖出高产田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁犁翻走低产洼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科学种田办样板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八字宪法”狠狠抓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨红花遍地开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争超“纲要”大步跨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红眼亮干劲大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤担子不觉重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山火海全不怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命当闯将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛鬼蛇神踩脚下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地当纸锄当笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的春天我们画！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}